overview: Lookout! Records presents this compilation of videos from their extensive pop-punk catalog that will have fans nostalgic for the old days. Gleefully raw and low-budget, the videos present the in-your-face attitude the genre once had. Clips include the The Queers ("Punk Rock Girls"), MTX ("Ba-Ba-Ba-Ba-Ba"), three videos by The Donnas before they hit it big, and more by Hi-Fives, Pattern, The Mr. T Experience, Pansy Division and others.
title: Turn-on, Tune-in, Lookout!
